{"tid":1289916,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(秒殺警察) 當年港督特赦大量「貪污警察」, 點解特首不能特赦反送中抗爭者?","createTime":"2019-07-06T09:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T03:14:27.000Z","uid":134071,"like":132,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"2269b1792c53d10682a519e0bd475930fb8b1844","tid":1289916,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/Wf39h1w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWf39h1w.jpg&h=5a297df2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7cbdd457b5337ff57f437a3cb7a352c8dc759f8","tid":1289916,"uid":134071,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:58:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkipadmin.org.hk/a/21874-chs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkipadmin.org.hk%2Fa%2F21874-chs&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjRT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=cf7d5c10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkipadmin.org.hk/a/21874-chs</a><br />\n<br />\n1974年，廉政公署成立取代香港警務處的反貪部，初期在對於警隊的調查，警隊被揭發出大量的貪污案件，被控涉嫌貪污的香港警務人員達260人，其中還發生了被拘留的警員畏罪自殺事件。由於牽連甚廣，使警隊內部人心惶惶，最終引起警員的不滿甚至仇視。1977年10月，2000余名警務人員在警察總部示威，要求削減廉政公署的權力。更一一批較激進的警員衝進廉政公署執行處，大肆搗亂及傷人。港英政府為了安撫警隊，不得不頒布&ldquo;局部特赦令&rdquo;，決定指令廉政公署特赦在1977年1月1日以前所有曾經貪污而未經檢控的公務員，同時即時修訂了《警務條例》，規定不接受命令和違反廉政公署條例的警員會被即時開除，這才使警員被逼就範。"},{"pid":"2e7774767d564ec7c3d4729466c76957f47171fa","tid":1289916,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:59:36.000Z","msg":"要利用黎反駁政府和警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1b85adaf09a6d8176fc47ef2e3f8bd5f147924","tid":1289916,"uid":122994,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />臭係，依家竟然有人吹緊一定要拉左告左先可以特赦<br />\n<br />\n出個行政命令就得架啦！"},{"pid":"22f0e24bb7198b88e61d5ed1f82afe6d3c1e2ed0","tid":1289916,"uid":134071,"li